                            android:layout_width="0dp"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                            android:text="\t\tWhen an Alchemist has mastered everything Alchemy has to teach them, they can learn Chemistry. Chemistry  Formulas create powerful alchemical concoctions. Given the right exotic material, Catalysts, time and the proper Formula, the Alchemist can make potions and elixirs that possess special and unique properties. Each Formula,  and all the requirements, are different and must be found in-game. A Chemist may brew 1 Chemistry item per  event per level of Chemistry. Chemistry is considered ‘ritual level’."
